<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_14_r3l22"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Erking<ex>er</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns / <expan>verſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / von deʒ Eſchenloers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_14_r3l23"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> / vnd des Heincʒen Swarcʒen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> <expan>armman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_14_r3l25">Davon <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir mit dem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> geredt / . vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_14_r3l27">vnd ſprichet / die güte cʒü 
<del rend="strikethrough">Pretheim </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_14_line_1574149428272_82">Preitfelt </ab></add> ſein 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_14_line_1574148875938_68">ſein </ab></add> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_14_r3l28">ſicʒ der in nücʒlıcher gewer / . Het <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> der ewr cʒü Jm iht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_14_r3l29">Darvmb wöll er Jm <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> eins <expan>frewntlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein vor des Reichs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_14_r3l30"><expan>Richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hıe cʒü <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / Het er <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü den <expan>güt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ıht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_14_r3l31">
<add><ab facs="#facs_14_r1l1">So möht </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ </del> er die für <expan>wende<ex>n</ex></expan> für das Lantgericht / <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> ſie <expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_14_r3l32">ſeın / . 
