<ab facs="#facs_14_r3l33">Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ . <expan>An<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Exaltac<ex>ionis</ex></expan> </ab>
