<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Sawnsheim czü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        Steffansberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Erking<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von dez Eschenloers,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, und des Heinczen Swarczen,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, davon
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir mit dem
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> geredt und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> und sprichet, die güte czü
                            <add>Preitfelt</add> sein <add>sein</add> und sicz der in nüczlicher
                        gewer. Het <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> der ewr czü im iht
                                <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darumb wöll er im
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> eins
                            <expan>frewntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hie czü
                            <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>. Het er <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        czü den <expan>güt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iht
                            <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <add>so möht</add> er die für
                                <expan>wende<ex>n</ex></expan> für das lantgericht
                                <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> sie <expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sein. <add><app>
<note><gap reason="damaged"/></note>
</app>ll er <app>
<note><gap reason="damaged"/></note>
</app>
<expan>t<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>, wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        erberkeit lieb und dienst <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>exaltac<ex>ionis</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan>
<expan>cruc<ex>is</ex></expan>. </ab></div>
